  "title": "Lord, teach us how to pray",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "Lord, teach"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "us"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "how to"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "pray,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Not as the nations"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "do in"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "vain,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "turn us"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "from our"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "way,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "cause us,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, to call on You each"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "day—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "Lord Jesus,"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "grow"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "in"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, You're the seed of life;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You've sown Yourself into our heart,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And now You have a start;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "So day by day more life to us impart—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, soften us;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You know the source from which we came."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "By calling on Your name,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, let no earth unturned nor rocks remain—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, how Your light makes clear"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we could not but e'er fail You;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yet there's a message true,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The seed of life within us will break through—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Make us in spirit poor;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, take whate'er we think we know."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We'll open to life's flow,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And thus take in the life that makes us grow—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, make us pure in heart;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For we'll be not content until"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "You all our being fill,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "O Lord, renew our mind, emotion, will—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Yes, Lord, impress our heart"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That we must take You in each day;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The seed will have its way;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Your growing brings the kingdom here to stay—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Amen!—The growth in life!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "There's nothing that Your life can't do;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Our every part renew."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We'll make it, we'll make it just by You."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord Jesus, grow in us."
            }
          ]
        }
